      <strong>Series:</strong>
      Book 3 in the Tales of Alvin Maker series
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Summary</strong>
    </p>
    <p xmlns="">
      A country schoolteacher and the child of a runaway slave
    find their destinies entwined with that of Alvin Miller, whose
    talent for "making" has marked him for destruction by the evil
    force known as the Unmaker. Card's epic tale of a magical,
    alternate America demonstrates his skill in graceful
    storytelling. Recommended, along with Seventh Son and Red
    Prophet , for most fantasy collections.-- JC
